aboutus.content: At JustSmart Custom Homes (JSCH), we believe that meticulous supervision is the only manner in which to build a truly custom home. We believe so strongly in this that a hands-on approach for all projects has become our philosophy.
What captures all buyers of a JSCH Home is the exceptional attention to the details that make their homes stand out among the rest.

Our promise to you is a one-of-a-kind custom home designed and built with the highest level of architectural talent, personalized service and top-of-the-line building materials. You will notice our innovative designs are elegant and stylish, while at the same time, comfortable and functional. We strive to achieve this important balance in all of our custom homes.

Creating exceptionally high-quality and distinctive custom homes is our passion. Unwavering commitment to you, our customer, is paramount. Our experienced team will work closely with you to ensure your vision is realized-and that the homebuilding experience is an enjoyable one. We are confident that you, like many of our other customers, will marvel at the level of service you will receive-even after moving into your new dream home.

JustSmartCustomHomes.name: Thorn Hills
JustSmartCustomHomes.mainDescr: Thornhill Addition in West Edmond is a unique neighborhood located off Danforth Road between Penn and Western Avenues. The construction began in 2005 with the idea that homeowners would have beautiful quality construction in Edmond with most of their square footage being on ground level or ALL on one level. The homes in the neighborhood are unique, because many different builders have added their touch to Thornhill over the years. Homes range anywhere from 2000 square feet to 5000 square feet depending which of the 5 sections of the neighborhood you are in.  The homeowners association fee covers the maintenance of entrances, a playground, basketball court, disc golf, and a greenbelt area. Thornhill is close by Frontier Elementary and Heartland Middle Schools in Edmond.
